abstract: "A multi-agent AI vessel routing system that combines hierarchical genetic algorithms (GA), mixed-integer linear programming (MILP), and LLM-coordinated agents to optimize global liner shipping networks. Generates profit-maximizing weekly service plans across 435 ports and 9,622 origin-destination lanes."
